    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>Il conte di palazzo Amedeo, <rs key="#Missus_regis">inviato</rs> in <rs
                            key="#Geographic_regions">Tuscia</rs> dall’<rs key="#Emperor/king"
                            >imperatore</rs>
                        <persName key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/136">Lamberto</persName>, siede
                        in giudizio <rs key="#Cities">civitate</rs>
                        <placeName ref="#places/2"
                            key="#Cities #Palatia #Viscount #Mother_churches #Bishops"
                            >Florencia</placeName> in <rs key="#Palatia">domum episcopii ipsius
                            civitatis</rs>, in atrio ante <orgName key="#Mother_churches"><rs
                                key="#Mother_churches">basilica</rs> Sancti Ioanni
                        Batista</orgName>, con il marchese Adalberto; assistono, fra gli altri, i
                            <rs key="#Bishops">vescovi</rs>
                        <persName key="#Bishops" ref="#people/138">Elbungo</persName> di <placeName
                            ref="#places/53" key="#Bishops">Parma</placeName>, <persName
                            key="#Bishops">Lupo</persName> di <placeName key="#Bishops"
                            ref="#places/164">Siena</placeName>, <persName key="#Bishops"
                            ref="#people/139">Odalberto</persName> di <placeName ref="#places/67"
                            key="#Bishops">Luni</placeName>, <persName key="#Bishops"
                            >Grasulfo</persName> di Firenze; i giudici imperiali Giovanni, Adalberto
                        e altro Adalberto; i <rs key="#vassusOf">vassalli marchionali</rs>
                        <persName key="#vassusOf" ref="#people/144">Winigildo</persName> del
                            <persName ref="#people/145">fu Furulo</persName>, <persName
                            key="#vassusOf" ref="#people/140">Rodilando</persName>, <persName
                            key="#vassusOf" ref="#people/141">Sichelmo</persName> e <persName
                            key="#vassusOf" ref="#people/142">Ghisalberto</persName>; <persName
                            key="#Viscount" ref="#people/143">Teudicio</persName>
                        <rs key="#Viscount">visconte</rs> ipsius civitatis; gli <rs key="#Scabini"
                            >scabini</rs> ipsius civitatis <persName key="#Scabini"
                            >Rotari</persName> e <persName key="#Scabini">Pietro</persName>. Si
                        presenta <persName key="#Bishops" ref="#people/213">Pietro</persName>, <rs
                            key="#Bishops">vescovo</rs> di <placeName ref="#places/4"
                            key="#Cities #Clusae/gates #Mother_churches #Bishops">Lucca</placeName>,
                        con il suo <rs key="#Advocatus_of_other_public_authorities">advocatus</rs>
                        <persName key="#Advocatus_of_other_public_authorities">Teuperto</persName>,
                        contestando alle seguenti persone beni che spettano al suo vescovato e che
                        essi tengono nescimus pro qua causa: i fratelli
                            <persName>Sisemundo</persName> e <persName>Offo</persName> tengono beni
                        a <placeName ref="#places/161">Valiano</placeName>; <persName
                            ref="#people/146">Adalfridi</persName> la <orgName key="#Churches"><rs
                                key="#Churches">chiesa</rs> di Santa Maria di <placeName
                                key="#Churches" ref="#places/163">Fereniano</placeName></orgName>
                        con le sue pertinenze e <rs key="#Manentes">5 manentes</rs> a <placeName
                            key="#Manentes">Ciciano</placeName>; <persName ref="#people/150"
                            key="#Consortes/shared_possessions">Fraolmi</persName> con i suoi <rs
                            key="#Consortes/shared_possessions">consortes</rs> beni prope <rs
                            key="#Cities">civitate</rs> Luca; i figli di
                            <persName>Autberto</persName>; <persName>C(...)d(...) de <placeName
                                ref="#places/167">Octavo</placeName></persName>;
                            <persName>Ragimbaldo de <placeName ref="#places/168"
                                >Fundannio</placeName></persName>; i figli di
                            <persName>Roppaldo</persName> beni ad <placeName ref="#places/169"
                            >Ancliana</placeName>; i figli di <persName>Filoardo</persName> beni in
                            <placeName ref="#places/170">Decimo</placeName> et in <placeName
                            ref="#places/171">Mozano</placeName>; <persName ref="#people/149"
                            >Cunimundo</persName> beni in <placeName ref="#places/1"
                            >Ilice</placeName> et in <placeName ref="#places/172">Flaviana seu in
                            Arcana</placeName>; il <rs key="#Other_clerics">chierico</rs>
                        <persName key="#Other_clerics">Andrea</persName> beni della <orgName
                            key="#Churches"><rs key="#Churches">chiesa</rs> di San Pietro
                            Somaldi</orgName>; <persName>Toto</persName> e
                            <persName>Ghervino</persName> il <orgName key="#Monasteries"><rs
                                key="#Monasteries">monastero</rs> di Santa Maria</orgName>; il
                        figlio di <persName>Petriperto</persName>; i figli di
                            <persName>Pietro</persName> beni in <placeName ref="#places/190"
                            >Garfaniana</placeName>; <persName>Atrialdo</persName> beni a
                            <placeName>Asanico</placeName>; i figli di <persName>Corrado</persName>
                        beni della <orgName key="#Churches"><rs key="#Churches">chiesa</rs> di Santa
                            Maria</orgName> qui est da <rs key="#Clusae/gates">porta Sancti
                            Donati</rs>; <persName>Toto</persName> figlio di
                            <persName>Corrado</persName> beni a <placeName ref="#places/175"
                            >Siviliano</placeName>; <persName>Omillo</persName> beni a <placeName
                            ref="#places/178">Ito</placeName> e in altri luoghi;
                            <persName>Willerado</persName> figlio di <persName>Pietro</persName>
                        beni a <placeName ref="#places/176">Castiliono</placeName> e in altri
                        luoghi; <persName>Roperto de <placeName ref="#places/185"
                                >Variana</placeName></persName> beni nello stesso luogo; il figlio
                        di <persName>Albone</persName> beni a <placeName ref="#places/186"
                            >Agello</placeName>; i figli di <persName>Widalgrimo</persName> beni a
                            <placeName>Crete</placeName>; <persName>Adalberto de <placeName
                                ref="#places/184">Capelle</placeName></persName>; il figlio di
                            <persName>Liutifrido</persName>; <persName>Ardimanno</persName>;
                            <persName>Ragimperto de <placeName>Fugiano</placeName></persName>; il
                            <rs key="#Priests">prete</rs>
                        <persName key="#Priests">Natale</persName>; <persName>Teudimundo</persName>;
                        i fratelli <persName>Ilpolfo</persName> e <persName>Bertaldo</persName>; il
                            <rs key="#Priests">prete</rs>
                        <persName key="#Priests">Sicardo</persName>; <persName>Bertaldo de
                                <placeName ref="#places/188">Suriano</placeName></persName> beni a
                            <placeName ref="#places/189">Campo Cassioli</placeName>; il <rs
                            key="#Other_clerics">chierico</rs>
                        <persName key="#Other_clerics">Baldo</persName>; i fratelli
                            <persName>Albone</persName> e <persName>Andrea</persName>;
                            <persName>Adalberto de <placeName ref="#places/187"
                                >Mangoniani</placeName></persName>; <persName>Roffridi</persName> la
                            <orgName key="#Churches"><rs key="#Churches">chiesa</rs> di <placeName
                                ref="#places/165">Sexto</placeName></orgName> con le sue pertinenze;
                        i figli di <persName ref="#people/151">Adaldo</persName> la <orgName
                            key="#Churches"><rs key="#Churches">chiesa</rs> di San
                            Terenzio</orgName> con le sue pertinenze; <persName>Warnerio</persName>
                        la <orgName key="#Churches"><rs key="#Churches">chiesa</rs> di San Michele
                            Arcangelo</orgName>; <persName>Ademari</persName>; il <rs
                            key="#Other_clerics">chierico</rs>
                        <persName key="#Other_clerics">Ghiselprando</persName> pertinenze della
                            <orgName key="#Churches"><rs key="#Churches">chiesa</rs> di San
                            Pietro</orgName>; il <rs key="#Priests">prete</rs>
                        <persName key="#Priests">Ghisolfo</persName> il <orgName key="#Monasteries"
                                ><rs key="#Monasteries">monastero</rs> di San Michele
                            Arcangelo</orgName>; <persName>Agliperto</persName> una casa;
                            <persName>Ato</persName> la <orgName key="#Churches"><rs key="#Churches"
                                >chiesa</rs> di San Nazario</orgName>; il <rs key="#Priests"
                            >prete</rs>
                        <persName key="#Priests">Ato</persName> e il <rs key="#Other_clerics"
                            >chierico</rs>
                        <persName key="#Other_clerics">Toto</persName> una casa;
                            <persName>Alamundo</persName>; <persName>Michele</persName>;
                            <persName>Teudilascio de <placeName ref="#places/181">Monte
                                Culacio</placeName></persName>; <persName>Anselmo de <placeName
                                ref="#places/182">Castaneclo</placeName></persName>;
                            <persName>Ato</persName>; <persName>Fraolmi de <placeName
                                ref="#places/179">Wammo</placeName></persName>;
                            <persName>Adalprando</persName>; il <rs>prete</rs>
                        <persName key="#Priests">Angelo</persName> un <rs key="#Monasteries"
                            >monastero</rs>; <persName>Willeramo de <placeName ref="#places/180"
                                >Vacule</placeName></persName>; <persName>Ateraldo de
                                <placeName>Placaio</placeName></persName>; <persName>Lamberto de
                                <placeName ref="#places/163">Fereniana</placeName></persName>;
                            <persName ref="#people/147">Lamberto</persName> che fu fratello di
                            <persName ref="#people/148">Rodilando</persName>;
                            <persName>Cunimundo</persName>; <persName>Raginfridi</persName> con i
                        suoi nepotes; i <rs key="#Priests">preti</rs>
                        <persName key="#Priests">Sindiperto</persName> e <persName key="#Priests"
                            >Benedetto</persName> la <orgName key="#Churches"><rs key="#Churches"
                                >chiesa</rs> di San Lorenzo di <placeName key="#Churches"
                                ref="#places/166">Tempaniano</placeName></orgName>, pertinenza
                            <orgName key="#Mother_churches">Sancti Ioanni Babtista</orgName>;
                            <persName>Giovanni de (...)</persName> la <orgName key="#Churches"><rs
                                key="#Churches">chiesa</rs> di San Lorenzo</orgName>. Il vescovo
                        chiede che costoro, i quali asseriscono di avere ricevuto i suddetti beni in
                            <rs key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">livello</rs>, si presentino e
                        dicano pro qua causa ipsas res detinent; sebbene chiamati per multus <rs
                            key="#Assembly">placitus</rs> presencia <rs key="#Missus_regis">missi
                            inperialis</rs> seu <rs key="#Count">comitum</rs> et modo per tres
                        civitatis presencia, costoro non si sono, infatti, mai presentati in
                        giudizio. Gli imputati, fatti cercare intus et foris eodem placito, sono
                        assenti anche in questa occasione; il vescovo viene, dunque, investito per
                        fuste dal conte di palazzo e dal marchese salva querimonia dei suddetti
                        beni, ad pars del <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/68"
                            key="#Mother_churches"><rs key="#Mother_churches">vescovato</rs> di San
                            Martino</orgName>. Il conte di palazzo e il marchese pongono sopra gli
                        stessi beni un <rs key="#Tuitio/bannum/mundeburdium">banno imperiale</rs> di
                            <rs key="#Penalty">2000 mancusi d’oro</rs>; metà da versare alla <rs
                            key="#Camera_regis">camera regia</rs>, metà ad pars del vescovato.
                        L’inviato e i giudici imperiali chiedono al <rs key="#Notary #Judge">notaio
                            e giudice imperiale</rs>
                        <persName key="#Notary #Judge">Leone</persName> la scrittura della noticia.
                        Sottoscrittori: <persName key="#Palatine_count #Missus_regis"
                            >Amedeo</persName>
                        <rs key="#Palatine_count">comes palacii</rs>, <persName
                            key="#Marquis/duke #Count">Adalberto</persName>
                        <rs key="#Count">comes</rs> et <rs key="#Marquis/duke">marchio</rs>,
                            <persName key="#Judge">Giovanni</persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudex domni imperatoris</rs>, <persName key="#Judge"
                            >Adalberto</persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudex domni imperatori</rs>, <persName key="#Judge"
                            >Adalberto</persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudex domni imperatoris</rs>.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
